### Adding New Folders
Add new folder cards in the Media Library section of `index.html`:

```html
<div class="folder-card">
    <div class="folder-thumbnail" style="background-image: url('YOUR_IMAGE_URL');">
        <span class="folder-badge badge-image">
            <!-- SVG icon -->
            Image
        </span>
    </div>
    <div class="folder-info">
        <!-- Folder details -->
    </div>
</div>
```

### Adding New Databases
Add new database cards in the Data Structures section:

```html
<div class="db-card">
    <div class="db-header">
        <!-- Database header -->
    </div>
    <div class="db-stats">
        <!-- Statistics -->
    </div>
    <div class="field-list">
        <!-- Field listings -->
    </div>
